High-Level Flow

[Provide user prompts in GHCP]

            ↓

[System Prompt Workflow]

            ↓

[.env Configuration]
              ↓
[Read INPUT_TYPE, INPUT_PATH, AUTH_TYPE]
              ↓
[Parse Swagger/OpenAPI Specification]
              ↓
[Generate Test Suite via Copilot]
    ├── Feature files (.feature)
    ├── Step definitions (*_steps.js)
    ├── API Helpers (*ApiHelper.js)
    ├── Data Models (*Models.js)
    └── Schema Validator (schemaValidator.js)
             ↓
[Execute Tests with Playwright]
    ├── Positive scenarios (200/201/204)
    ├── Negative scenarios (400/401/404/500)
    └── Schema validation (GET always, POST/PUT conditionally)
             ↓
[Retry Logic - 3 attempts per scenario]
            ↓
[Generate Reports]
    ├── Cucumber HTML/JSON (/reports/)
    ├── Allure Dashboard (/allure-report/)
    └── TEST_SUMMARY.md (Comprehensive markdown)
